<div class="hero">
  <img class="hero__logo" src="/images/post_logo.png" alt="POST logo - Meet POST Bot"/>
  <h1 class="hero__text">Meet POST Bot &ndash;</br>
  the easiest way to get valuable feedback on your Articles</h1>
  <%= render "action.html", current_team: @current_team, conn: @conn %>
</div>

<div class="bottom">
  <div class="bottom__offset container">
    <h2 class="bottom__title">How POST works:</h2>
    <ul class="steps">
      <li class="steps__item">
        <div class="steps__left">
          <img class="steps__image" src="/images/step-1.svg" alt="Step 1 - Send POST Bot your Article"/>
        </div>
        <div class="steps__right">
          <h3 class="steps__title">1. Send POST Bot your Article</h3>
          <p class="steps__description">
            Simply paste your articleâ€™s URL in a Slack message to POST Bot and the Bot gets to work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="steps__item">
        <div class="steps__left">
          <img class="steps__image" src="/images/step-2.svg" alt="Step 2 - POST tracks your article"/>
        </div>
        <div class="steps__right">
          <h3 class="steps__title">2. POST tracks your article</h3>
          <p class="steps__description">
            POST starts tracking your article over the course of several hours and analyzes how it preforms for you
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="steps__item">
        <div class="steps__left">
          <img class="steps__image" src="/images/step-3.svg" alt="Step 3 - Get notifications"/>
        </div>
        <div class="steps__right">
          <h3 class="steps__title">3. Get notifications</h3>
          <p class="steps__description">
            When POST notices something going on with your article it will notify you via Slack, and even recommend actions for you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="try">
      <%= if is_nil(@current_team) do %>
        <h3 class="try__title">Try POST now:</h3>
      <% end %>
      <%= render "action.html", current_team: @current_team, conn: @conn %>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <p>Have feedback or questions? Contact us</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</div>
